Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's fine if you decide to\Nhead right on back here, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to take care of Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys care take of yourselves, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you to both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye out for the good news I'll be sending!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, we're off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These new adventurers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Welling up inside them is courage, wit, and curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On their path, hope and despair alike are lying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:01:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daremo ga sakaraezu ni mogutteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.79,0:01:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono me o tomoshibi yori kagayakasete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezasu saki wa fukaku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Massugu ni mayoikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuchiaketa naraku no wana
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.29,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu no ato o oikakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ima kotae ga mitsukaru nara zenbu nakushitemo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sono koe o hanasanai youni kodama ga mada hibiiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rashinban wa zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yami o sashita mama
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nigeba no nai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sore ga noroi demo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodou wa honmono
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:02:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nidoto akogare wa tomaranai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Reg... wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder when I drifted off to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that... Your belly was just so warm, Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We hardly ever stay up that late, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you have any idea where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We dropped directly down from the Wharf District,\Nbut I couldn't really say what area we're in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The depth gauge is indicating 820 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way brighter here than up on the surface, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Rock Ark, located at a depth of 600 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so far above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long ago, I was aiming for a depth of 400 meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and now we can't even see it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, due to the distortion in the force field,\Nwe can't see the surface, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That boundary looks awfully bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that distortion carrying the light downward?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrific, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At this pace we can make it\Nto the bottom of the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we can't let our guard down, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We might even make it all way to the second layer\Nbefore anyone comes after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,W-well that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have some breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take out the demonfish innards\Nmaking sure not to damage them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and smoke them to keep as preserved food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the meat, put a hearty helping in a pot and\Nsprinkle a bit of ground-up Eternal Fortunes on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mix in some stick miso, and then once you throw in\Na bunch of diced sainona greens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! My special "Riko Soup" is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Irredeemable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it tastes better than Riko Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, what's that you're playing around with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my Star Compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, something that helps you tell up from down...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong! It points to the bottom of the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not magnetic or weighted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you shake it or rotate it around,\Nthe direction of the needle doesn't budge a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.58,0:06:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Relic of the Abyss, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling there's some\Nincomprehensible principle at work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, is that thing really even useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's fine, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an old saying:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All that which is taken from the Abyss\Nwill someday be returned to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it be an object or a life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Abyss is greedy like that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachings of cave raiders are quite humble...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Leader taught that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We were rushing around so much I forgot all about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,An envelope...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, go ahead and take a look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother's sealed letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, did you make off with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The pages we saw last time were tattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is probably just a copy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we left the orphanage,\NI actually bumped into Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I really had him fooled, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly realized that thing\Nwas in my back pocket, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's pretty much the only one\Nwho could've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader... I wonder if he's cheering us on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a page that's a different size than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll depart at dawn to come capture you"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, do you have any idea\Nhow long it's been since dawn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, considering that it was already bright out\Nwhen we woke up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We've gotta get going quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, go hide any traces of the campfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,go check that we're not leaving anything behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiggy said that if we make it to the second layer,\Nno one will come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why would Leader\Ndo something so contrary to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be testing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our final lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is that if we get caught now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we never had any chance of making it\Nto the bottom of the netherworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Silkfangs can't leave their territory! It'll act as an anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What an irredeemable plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it gave up and let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm okay. I'm just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not used to this,\Nso I bet it's really draining her stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her first time this deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on an untracked path...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and on top of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems our pursuers still haven't caught up with us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've strayed from the usual route...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so even if they come after us,\Nthey won't find us that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the search parties\Nmove in groups of at least three people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so we should see them com-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The break in the clouds there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the second layer: the Forest of Temptation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the second layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If a Red Whistle goes down there,\Nit's treated as a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My own voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The view's so amazing I just kinda collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, let's take a little break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take a pee, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, then I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko, I was thinking about your delusion\Nabout the meaning of the letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,About it being our final lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I have a feeling you're not mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader said it's necessary for him to patrol every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he was able to see through us\Nand uncover our nightly plotting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the fact that I'm a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, if he took the trouble\Nto place that envelope in my pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to make a clean escape\Nand show him we're up to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Reg?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Something flashed over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was around that group of three boulders up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you think it's a search party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a cave raider!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just one of them...\Nbut he's heading straight for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We even took care to stay off the usual route...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking the trouble to head down this\Nway off the main route...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt he's targeting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you see our pursuer anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to look now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Think we can give him the slip\Nbefore we reach the second layer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... right above us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? He's way too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's caught up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we somehow slip away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less from Lyza's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty darn fast, huh, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Habo?! But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some skills of my own, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Whistle Hablog...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To think someone who's not a White Whistle\Ncould be so skilled...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I could let Riko escape alone first...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That being said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I never suspected it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That you were a supreme treasure\Nof the netherworld, I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is even your skin a Relic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure can't tell just by looking at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing mechanical about those balls of yours, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop kicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking into account the weight of your backpack,\Nyou're pretty darn light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he still hasn't learned the hand signals...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't told you what I'm here about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see... I'm not actually here to capture you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nat and Shiggy came and paid me a visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to take them all the way\Nto the Seeker Camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just at least help them escape to the second layer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this is your last chance to see the true form\Nof a supreme treasure of the netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg was really fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm sure, Habo, with your speed you can cat-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me Reg is truly a\Ntreasure of the netherworld, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.29,0:15:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see, I came to pay my respects\Nto this "supreme treasure of the netherworld."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish paying your respects was the only thing you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the search party\Nwas looking for you by the Twisting Crag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose they'll take a while still.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had a look at the treasure of the netherworld,\Nso I better fulfill my promise to those boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming along with you to the Seeker Camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be reassuring to have a Black Whistle with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Riko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Habo... uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I can't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This right here... is our final lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty clever of him, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if this is indeed your final lesson,\NI won't get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But he should have come himself\Nto see you off one last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but that wouldn't work\N'cause he'd catch you right away then, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Habo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all the way down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have some other business down here, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vaccine for the second layer\Nthat Blue Whistles and up take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll generally spare you from picking up\Nthe diving illness down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, these are left over from yesterday, but here's\Nsome mustard steamed buns to keep you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't wait too long to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Habo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lastly, and also most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I won't be accompanying you any further,\NI should tell you this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,About that monitoring base\Ncalled Seeker Camp you're headed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the guardian there is a bit of a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the person who found\Nthe sealed letter from my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Unmovable Sovereign, "Ozen the Immovable"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a White Whistle who's still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After you were born in the depths of the Abyss,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,she's the one who carried you\Nto the surface along with Lyza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A White Whistle?! And the very one who saved my life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Hablog, that doesn't seem like anything\Nto be too worried about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be wary of the White Whistle, Ozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't personally go into the details,\Nbut Riko might encounter some distressing things there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright! I'd like to meet a White Whistle, in any case!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And stuff about my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and about the time when\Nshe found my mom's sealed letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta ask about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a reassuring partner with you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, take care of Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're heading out now, Habo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you dawdle around I'll become a White Whistle\Nand catch up to you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Give my best to Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we're all just the netherworld's lost children...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, I knew this day would come...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reg, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wind-riding windmill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago they used those\Nto capture updrafts, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear they've been around for more than 4,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They've done well to last so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we've passed by them means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the depths' second layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, Reg!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We've survived our final lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader, we pulled it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't really hit me yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we really get away from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to worry about anyone\Npursuing us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If we descend down this far,\Nno help will be sent after us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because both heading here\Nand returning home become very difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite sure that's what Shiggy said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words, down here even the search party\Nwould find that it itself is the one being pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry on, Reg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be calling all of its buddies over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that we've successfully escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it rather that we're now being pursued by\Nall kinds of things that exist outside the territory of man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora ni ukanderu hikaru nami o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tabanete niji no hashi o kakeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaui ashiba, suberu slope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako to mirai no michishirube
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi no hidarite, boku no migite o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunaide tsunagete hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Itsumo soba ni iru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kako mo ima mo mirai mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dakara mayowazu ni aruiteikou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:23:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Irotoridori no yume kasanete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.83,0:23:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashita wa doko ni mukau
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimi to issho ni iretara, sekai wa kagayakidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saihate no chi ni saku hana o sagasou
